[14]
*
(Please type a command or say `\end')
*ProofZoom is a curated collection of concise expository essays on important ma
thematical proofs. Each essay has two aims: to present the main proof with eleg
ance and clarity, and to reveal the hidden steps where readers are most likely 
to stumble.

*
(Please type a command or say `\end')
*Many mathematical proofs are correct but compressed. The central idea may be b
uried under technical detail, or a crucial local step may be passed over too qu
ickly. ProofZoom addresses both problems.

*
(Please type a command or say `\end')
*Each entry presents the central idea behind the proof, explains the mechanism 
that makes the proof work, and gives a clear derivation. When a proof contains 
a local pain point, a PZoom box may provide an optional zoom-in: a hidden sub-p
roof that readers can open when they want the missing detail.

*
(Please type a command or say `\end')
*Thus ProofZoom serves as both a conceptual guide and a proof companion: it kee
ps the main argument readable while making the difficult steps available exactl
y where they are needed.

*
(Please type a command or say `\end')
*Mission

*
(Please type a command or say `\end')
*ProofZoom offers elegant, go-to expositions of fundamental mathematical result
s, with optional zoom-ins that resolve the local pain points hidden inside conc
ise proofs.

*
(Please type a command or say `\end')
